data.description: Welcome home to the Guard Gated Community of Copper Creek! A corner lot with lots of space to grow! This 3 bedroom 3 bath 2 car garage has everything you need to live in Vegas! All tile downstairs living, dining and kitchen area for busy traffic days. Granite countertops in the kitchen and a pantry, the upstairs master bedroom has double sinks and shower, walk in closet. The backyard is finished with concrete and the community has tons of features including a Clubhouse, Pool, Play Ground, Exercise Room, and Basketball Courts Fresh Paint and carpet being finished up!
